      "type": "p",
      "text": "A basic example of collecting user input, using it to fill a LLM prompt template, then sending the result to the LLM for response generation. The response is then streamed back to the user in real-time via MarkdownStream()."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "To learn more, see the article on Gen AI streaming."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "This particular template uses chatlas.ChatAnthropic() to do response generation via Anthropic. With chatlas, it’s easy to switch to other providers. Just change ChatAnthropic() to another provider (e.g., ChatOpenAI())."
    },
